      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BROTHER MOUNTAIN (6) comes through the Nutrien Classic Sales series at Wagga where he placed in the heats before he came from this barrier for a solid fifth in the final at Listed level. The class drop suits and he should be at peak fitness fourth up. SPIRITED GIGI (4) has improved with each start this time in and gave a sight last time when he led from this barrier and stuck on for third in the Graduation Series 3YO Trot Final at Maryborough. Has placed in both attempts here. Could peak and win. TRUSCOTTS ELEGANCE (8) was last seen when midfield in the G1 Vicbred Super Series 2F Final six-and-a-half months ago. Has placed in half of her 10 starts here and she draws for a trail. MISTER DEVEREAUX (1) made an encouraging return when runner-up from a wider barrier at Geelong. Steps out of maiden grade but he'll strip fitter and gets the inside draw.",
